<font color="#FF0000">TREAT THE VNW WITH HONESTY</font><br>
<tt>Thu Dec  5 22:54:26 US/Eastern 1996
</tt><p>
The Vietnam War should be treated in schools with honesty, pretty or ugly. <br><br>
It was not a war of national glory, just a lot of individual and very personal heroism, sacrifice, and trauma.<br><br>
It is easy to rewrite history.<br><br>
Invite a few Vietnam Veterans to speak to the students. There are enough of us around who would be willing to speak and answer questions. We are more real than anything in any history book!<br><br>

